# Global Styles and Tailwind CSS

Global styles are defined in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css). This file includes Tailwind CSS directives and custom CSS variables for theming (light/dark mode).

Tailwind CSS is configured in [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) and [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts). PostCSS configuration is in [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js) and [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs).
